details: The Ballistics Filter Designer module creates IIR coefficients that describe one-sided smoothing for a control signal, constraining how quickly a value can rise or fall. Useful for building meters, envelopes, and dynamics displays with physically realistic response curves.
author: AudioBench
title: Ballistics Filter Designer
overview: Generates IIR coefficients for smoothing a control signal by and amount in dB and speed in seconds.
